When debugging Runa:

Use the built-in debugger with LLM tracing
Enable verbose semantic analysis
Check translation accuracy reports
Verify against formal grammar spec
Test with multiple target languages

Debug commands:
bashruna debug --semantic --trace program.runa
runa validate --grammar program.runa

runa translate --verify program.runa --to python,js,rust